# 🛒 SuperShop Management System (MVC)

A **Java Swing desktop application** for managing a retail shop, built with the **MVC (Model-View-Controller)** architecture pattern. Developed as a CSE 202: Object Oriented Programming I Lab project at **University of Asia Pacific**.

