## ✨ Features

### 🔐 Authentication
- Role-based login system — separate access for **Admin** and **Employee**
- Secure password authentication via `AuthController`
- Auto-creates a default admin account if no data file exists

### 👤 Admin Panel
- **Employee Management** — Add, update, and delete employee accounts
- **Inventory Management** — Add Standard and Discount items, update details, delete items, restock
- **Item Search** — Search inventory by Item ID or Item Name
- **Sales Report** — View all billing transactions made today

### 🧾 Employee Panel
- **Browse Inventory** — View all available items with live stock and pricing
- **Billing / Cart** — Add items to cart, update quantities, remove items
- **Invoice Generation** — Formatted customer invoice printed on checkout
- **Stock Auto-Update** — Inventory stock reduces automatically after each sale

### 💾 Data Persistence
- All data saved to **CSV files** — survives application restarts
- Separate files for employees, items, and invoices

