## 📁 Project Structure

```
MVC/
├── Main.java                          # Application entry point
│
├── models/                            # M — Model layer
│   ├── User.java                      # Abstract base class for users
│   ├── Admin.java                     # Admin user (extends User)
│   ├── Employee.java                  # Employee user (extends User)
│   ├── Item.java                      # Abstract base class for items
│   ├── StandardItem.java              # Regular priced item (extends Item)
│   ├── DiscountItem.java              # Discounted item (extends Item)
│   └── Bill.java                      # Shopping cart & invoice model
│
├── controllers/                       # C — Controller layer
│   ├── AuthController.java            # Handles login & session
│   ├── UserController.java            # Employee CRUD operations
│   ├── InventoryController.java       # Item CRUD, search, stock management
│   └── BillingController.java         # Cart management & invoice generation
│
├── view/                              # V — View layer (Java Swing GUI)
│   ├── LoginFrame.java                # Login window
│   ├── AdminDashboard.java            # Admin main screen
│   ├── EmployeeDashboard.java         # Employee main screen
│   ├── AddEmployeeDialog.java         # Dialog: add new employee
│   ├── UpdateEmployeeDialog.java      # Dialog: edit employee
│   ├── AddItemDialog.java             # Dialog: add new item
│   ├── UpdateItemDialog.java          # Dialog: edit item
│   ├── SearchItemDialog.java          # Dialog: search items
│   ├── BillingDialog.java             # Dialog: cart & checkout
│   └── SalesReportDialog.java         # Dialog: today's sales report
│
├── dao/                               # Data Access Object layer
│   └── CSVHandler.java                # All CSV file read/write operations
│
└── data/                              # Auto-generated data files
    ├── employees.csv                  # User accounts
    ├── items.csv                      # Inventory
    └── invoices.csv                   # Billing history
```

---

## 🏗️ Architecture Overview

This project strictly follows the **MVC pattern**:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      VIEW                           │
│  LoginFrame │ AdminDashboard │ EmployeeDashboard    │
│  Dialogs (Add/Update/Search/Billing/SalesReport)    │
└────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┘
                         │ calls
┌────────────────────────▼────────────────────────────┐
│                   CONTROLLER                        │
│  AuthController │ UserController                    │
│  InventoryController │ BillingController            │
└──────────┬──────────────────────────┬───────────────┘
           │ uses                     │ persists via
┌──────────▼──────────┐   ┌───────────▼───────────────┐
│       MODEL         │   │          DAO               │
│  User / Admin /     │   │      CSVHandler            │
│  Employee           │   │  (employees.csv,           │
│  Item / Standard /  │   │   items.csv,               │
│  DiscountItem       │   │   invoices.csv)            │
│  Bill               │   └───────────────────────────┘
└─────────────────────┘
```

