## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Java JDK **21 or higher** installed
- Any Java IDE (IntelliJ IDEA recommended) **or** command-line tools

### Run with IntelliJ IDEA
1. Clone or download this repository
2. Open IntelliJ IDEA → **File → Open** → select the `MVC/` folder
3. Wait for the project to index
4. Open `Main.java`
5. Click the **▶ Run** button (or press `Shift + F10`)

### Run from Command Line
```bash
# Navigate to the project root
cd MVC

# Compile all source files
javac -d out/production/MVC \
  Main.java \
  models/*.java \
  dao/*.java \
  controllers/*.java \
  view/*.java

# Run the application
java -cp out/production/MVC Main
```

> **Note:** The `data/` folder and CSV files are created automatically on first run.

